summary: Comprehensive frontend testing completed for Mediterranean boat rental multi-page website. React Router navigation, UI components, mobile responsiveness, and all key features tested successfully.

integration_issues.issue: One footer link navigation test experienced timeout, but links are present and functional

passed_tests: Home page loads with hero carousel, fleet section, FAQ accordion, stats bar, CTA section
Navbar shows all 5 page links (Home, Itinerari, Prezzi, Prenotazioni, Contatti)
React Router navigation works between all pages
Itinerari page loads with hero and placeholder content
Prezzi page loads with hero and placeholder content
Prenotazioni page loads with FareHarbor and WhatsApp CTAs
Contatti page loads with Google Maps embed and contact info
Mobile hamburger menu opens Sheet with navigation links
WhatsApp floating button visible on all pages
Footer shows navigation links using React Router
All CTA buttons have correct FareHarbor and WhatsApp links
Language switcher flags (IT, EN, FR, DE) are functional
success_percentage: Frontend: 95% - Nearly all features working correctly
